The USB-PD VDM DFU-trigger implementation in
crates/restorekit/src/dfu/vdm.rs is a Rust port of macvdmtool
(https://github.com/AsahiLinux/macvdmtool), Copyright The Asahi Linux
Contributors, which is itself based on ThunderboltPatcher
(https://github.com/osy/ThunderboltPatcher), Copyright 2019 osy86. Both are
licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

This product bundles, as git submodules built from source, the following
libraries, each under its own license (see each project for details):
libplist, libimobiledevice-glue, libusbmuxd, libirecovery, libtatsu,
libimobiledevice, and idevicerestore (libimobiledevice project, LGPL-2.1);
and libzip (https://libzip.org, BSD-3-Clause).
